                <span class=""><p>I made the recipe for these that is in the &quot;Cookies&quot; book.  In the picture, the cookies appeared to be sort of domed on the top. Mine come out on the flatter side  - not totally flat, but flatter than the picture.  Might this be from not leaving enough space between the cookies?</p>
</span>            </div>
            <span class="field-content"></span>                      </li>                    <li>
            <div class="commenter">
                <span class="field-content"><span class="username">barbarajl</span></span>            </div>

